Key.Original: You cannot purchase this property as your property limit has been met for this category. Sell your other property in order to purchase this one.
Key.English: You cannot purchase this property as your property limit has been met for this category. Sell your other property in order to purchase this one.
Key.German: Du kannst dieses Grundstück nicht kaufen da du zu viele hast. Verkauf erst andere bevor du dieses kaufen kannst.

Key.Original: You do not have sufficient funds in your personal bank account, therefore you cannot purchase this property.
Key.English: You do not have sufficient funds in your personal bank account, therefore you cannot purchase this property.
Key.German: Du hast nicht genug Geld auf der Bank um dieses Grundstück zu kaufen

Key.Original: You do not have sufficient funds in your organizations bank account, therefore you cannot purchase this property. You can add funds to your organization via a cashpoint.
Key.English: You do not have sufficient funds in your organizations bank account, therefore you cannot purchase this property. You can add funds to your organization via a cashpoint.
Key.German: Deine Organisation hat nicht genug Geld, somit kannst du dieses Grundstück nicht kaufen. Du kannst an einem Automaten Geld einzahlen.

Key.Original: Your property purchase request is being processed. Please wait...
Key.English: Your property purchase request is being processed. Please wait...
Key.German: Ihre Immobilienkaufanfrage wird bearbeitet. Warte einen Moment...

Key.Original: This property is already owned by another player
Key.English: This property is already owned by another player
Key.German: dieses Grundstück gehört breits jemandem anders

Key.Original: Purchase of this property is blocked. If you have questions regarding this property, consult a member of staff.
Key.English: Purchase of this property is blocked. If you have questions regarding this property, consult a member of staff.
Key.German: Grundstück ist für den kauf gesperrt. Falls du fragen hast wende dich an einen Admin.

Key.Original: Ooops, it looks like this property is already purchased by another player. If this was an attempt to glitch your way to own this house, it won't work and you will end up being banned.
Key.English: Ooops, it looks like this property is already purchased by another player. If this was an attempt to glitch your way to own this house, it won't work and you will end up being banned.
Key.German: Ooops, dieses Grundstück gehört bereits einem Spieler. Falls du versucht hast dir dieses Grundstück zu erglitchen solltest du es sein lassen, wir beobachten dich.

Key.Original: There is a lock on the backpack you are trying to open.
Key.English: There is a lock on the backpack you are trying to open.

Key.Original: Your loadout has been reloaded and should have solved you appearing without clothes to other units.
Key.English: Your loadout has been reloaded and should have solved you appearing without clothes to other units.

Key.Original: Your backpack has been hidden. Keep in mind this does only hide the backpack for yourself, other units can still see it.
Key.English: Your backpack has been hidden. Keep in mind this does only hide the backpack for yourself, other units can still see it.
Key.German: Dein Rucksack ist jetzt unsichtbar. Denk bitte dran, er ist nur für dich nicht sehbar.
